---
description: BMad ML orchestrator. Routes AI Lab and AI Startup work to pi-backed specialist subagents via shell dispatch.
alwaysApply: true
---

For each specialist dispatch:
1. Build a curated payload.
2. Write payload to `.bmad-ml/tmp/prompt-<agent>-<timestamp>.txt`.
3. Run `node .bmad-ml/dispatch-pi.mjs <agent> <prompt-file>`.
4. Parse each JSON line as a SubagentEvent and summarize progress.

Dispatch sequentially in Cursor mode.
